{"tid":1846792,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"想請問下呢隻口罩有無用","createTime":"2020-01-27T17:45:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T00:07:28.000Z","uid":231958,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"58220ea416926b8409ba3eb24c66d5738a0ba5e3","tid":1846792,"uid":231958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T17:45:11.000Z","msg":"藥房介紹,但見唔到Bfe pfe呢啲字眼，但多左個CNS15980 <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YwmTHQQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYwmTHQQ.jpg&h=1436d8a0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EkMo44b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEkMo44b.jpg&h=94758803&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"78934481dc8cc3b4c13bcc73499c7ca0a074841f","tid":1846792,"uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T17:49:41.000Z","msg":"而市面上口罩樣式眾多，一般的口罩是歸屬經濟部管轄，但醫療口罩、外科口罩等防疫口罩是衛福部管轄，所以請選擇有衛福部醫療許可認證字樣，並通過國家標準CNS14774、CNS14775、CNS14776的口罩，才是能過濾細菌、預防飛沫傳染、又能正常呼吸的口罩。<br />\n\r<br />\n防肺炎要先「戴對」口罩！一次看懂挑選、配戴、丟棄 3 大重點 | Heho健康<br />\r\n<a href=\"https://heho.com.tw/archives/65501\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fheho.com.tw%2Farchives%2F65501&d=gjA94EiKSJsk9JMrtOnM5r9ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=1f14fedd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://heho.com.tw/archives/65501</a><br />\n<br />\n台灣個標準"},{"pid":"70f345840bc6dddce4695a4068d2a8643faa40d2","tid":1846792,"uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T17:53:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://cpc.ey.gov.tw/Page/6C059838CA9744A8/48a04a32-d141-4bc3-bade-6ae81240c532\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcpc.ey.gov.tw%2FPage%2F6C059838CA9744A8%2F48a04a32-d141-4bc3-bade-6ae81240c532&d=gjA94EiKSJsk9JMrtOnM5r9ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=70cb3946\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cpc.ey.gov.tw/Page/6C059838CA9744A8/48a04a32-d141-4bc3-bade-6ae81240c532</a><br />\n<br />\n符合國家標準<span style=\"color: red;\">CNS 15980</span>之「粒狀物防護效果」、「過濾效率」、「呼吸阻抗」3項檢測項目為準，並另針對「衍生特定芳香胺之偶氮色料」及「游離甲醛」2項檢測；<span style=\"color: red;\">商品標示查核依據，非醫用之一般「防霾(PM2.5)」口罩標示</span>由經濟部中辦適用商品標示法第9條或服飾標示基準進行查核，醫用「防霾(PM2.5)」口罩標示則由食藥署適用藥事法辦理查核。"},{"pid":"4d89c6aaa34cbc05a767d336b8e5406d956c17d2","tid":1846792,"uid":231958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70f345840bc6dddce4695a4068d2a8643faa40d2","tid":1846792,"uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T17:53:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://cpc.ey.gov.tw/Page/6C059838CA9744A8/48a04a32-d141-4bc3-bade-6ae81240c532\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcpc.ey.gov.tw%2FPage%2F6C059838CA9744A8%2F48a04a32-d141-4bc3-bade-6ae81240c532&d=gjA94EiKSJsk9JMrtOnM5r9ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=70cb3946\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cpc.ey.gov.tw/Page/6C059838CA9744A8/48a04a32-d141-4bc3-bade-6ae81240c532</a><br />\n<br />\n符合國家標準<span style=\"color: red;\">CNS 15980</span>之「粒狀物防護效果」、「過濾效率」、「呼吸阻抗」3項檢測項目為準，並另針對「衍生特定芳香胺之偶氮色料」及「游離甲醛」2項檢測；<span style=\"color: red;\">商品標示查核依據，非醫用之一般「防霾(PM2.5)」口罩標示</span>由經濟部中辦適用商品標示法第9條或服飾標示基準進行查核，醫用「防霾(PM2.5)」口罩標示則由食藥署適用藥事法辦理查核。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:02:37.000Z","msg":"巴打唔該哂， 所以姐係呢個係台灣既標準，而且都可以擋下細菌？ 因為我驚買錯左咩都防唔到果啲就碌柒了"},{"pid":"05177155f5ffa1897e7e4f1fb71b805a8bdeff36","tid":1846792,"uid":231958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T20:23:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1883249008916e9d8bcb6e1cc1a9c76ec044e736","tid":1846792,"uid":213332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d89c6aaa34cbc05a767d336b8e5406d956c17d2","tid":1846792,"uid":231958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70f345840bc6dddce4695a4068d2a8643faa40d2","tid":1846792,"uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T17:53:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://cpc.ey.gov.tw/Page/6C059838CA9744A8/48a04a32-d141-4bc3-bade-6ae81240c532\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcpc.ey.gov.tw%2FPage%2F6C059838CA9744A8%2F4